cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use realtime-calib in your research, please cite it."
title: "realtime-calib: real-time multi-camera calibration"
abstract: >-
  A local, real-time, open-source multi-camera calibration application. It
  recovers the intrinsics and 6-DoF extrinsics of a rig of USB cameras, is driven
  from a responsive web app on any device (single-pass capture and calibration,
  usable on headless Linux servers), and exports Caliscope-compatible and
  engine-ready calibration files.
type: software
authors:
